Package com.complexible.common.util.concurrent.locks

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExclusiveLock
    Interface for a lock which is exclusive.
    MultiLock
    Provides nonreenterant locking capability for a given ID.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractLock2
    Abstract base implementation of Lock
    BroadMultiLock
    Implementation of MultiLock interface with broad locking feature which means a thread might block for an ID even tough that ID is not locked by another thread but a different ID is locked.
    Locks
    Utility class for working with locks
    PreciseMultiLock
    Implementation of MultiLock interface with precise locking which means no thread will block for an ID unless that ID is locked by another thread.
    SimpleMultiLock
    Implementation of MultiLock interface with precise locking which means no thread will block for an ID unless that ID is locked by another thread.
